  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "The Game Boy Advance version of Spider-Man 3, a videogame based on the 2007 movie of the same name.\n\nThe Game Boy Advance version is a level-based 2D side-scrolling beat 'em up; only the characters are rendered in 2.5D. A map is used to enter levels, and each level has question bubbles that give hints.",
